# Networks Project 2021 / 370-Project

## About / Synopsis

* This is a networks project implemented for a college class. This project blocks a user from accessing a website based on its IP address. 

## Installation

* Install Python 3 https://www.python.org/downloads/
* Pip install httpserver https://pypi.org/project/httpserver/ 
* Pip install scapy https://scapy.readthedocs.io/en/latest/installation.html
* Pip install asyncio https://pypi.org/project/asyncio/

## Usage
* Type python Hosts_File_Filter.py to run the hosts file filter. 
* Type python DNS_Proxy.py to run the DNS proxy server. 

### Requirements

Python 3. 


### Limitations

The DNS Proxy server can only intercept DNS requests and cannot return the spoofed packets to the client process. 
